arStrings.szText: Poor Marta...she had what we call gut rot. A nice name for a horrible affliction. She should have sent you with a message rather than coming all this way. Now she's dead and given us gut rot as a parting gift.
Make up for bringing her here in the first place. Do what I would have done, were I not sick.
Go to Pilgrim's Cave â€”harvest the Gano Fungus that grows on the creatures that live there and bring it to me.
